^5Help - Wizcast
~5USAGE: .wizcast ^5message
~5WHERE: ^5message ~5is something you wish to say to other wizards

~5Use this command when you want to send a message to only the Wizards and
~5Gods that are online.  By itself, it will review the last several wizcasts.

~5EXAMPLES
  ~5.wizcast
  ~5.wizcast Hello fellow high ranking officials!

